    <step order="5">Add new optional props to `NarrativeBullet`: `onCheck?(id): void`, `onRemove?(id): void`, `onKeep?(id, currentTtlSeconds): void`. If undefined, hide the button (defensive default)</step>
    <step order="6">Plumb the new props through `ActivityNotesSection.tsx` from its parent</step>
